sentences: Fumitoshi Ishino (石野 文敏, Ishino Fumitoshi, born 26 December 1967), better known by his stage name Takkyu Ishino (石野 卓球, Ishino Takkyū), is a Japanese DJ, record producer, and singer from Shizuoka, Shizuoka Prefecture.
